name: GreenTronics Design
overview:
GreenTronics Design Labs India Pvt. Ltd. is a Private Limited business venture, which was established in the year 2012 at Bengaluru, Karnataka. We are among the most reputed manufacturers and suppliers of the market engaged in offering an extensive range of Solar Lighting Solutions, Energy Recorders, Light Bulb Units, Grid Chargers, Solar Panels, Extension Cables and LED Lightings. Our experts use advanced production techniques and high-grade materials to develop these products.

Infrastructure: We boast a sound infrastructural building, which is constructed over a large area of land at Bengaluru, Karnataka. It is divided into different departments, which are resourced with state-of-the-art facilities. Our in-house manufacturing unit is operational with technologically advanced machinery. This help us produce immaculate product line for the clients in large quantities at fast pace.

Our Team: Our dexterous team of qualified and trained professionals enables us to efficiently cater to the variegated demands of different industries based across the country.

Quality: We quality test each and every product on well defined parameters prior to the final dispatch to our esteemed clients. Our experts employ modern production techniques and high-grade materials to develop highly reliable products for the clients. We source our production materials from the certified and authentic vendors of the market. We practice stringent quality control system in our manufacturing process, in order to ensure maximum benefits of the clients.

Our Products: Solar Lighting Solutions, Energy Recorders, Light Bulb Units, Grid Chargers, Solar Panels, Extension Cables and LED Lightings.
